model.chess_set

Class Piece

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.chess_set.Piece
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bishop, King, Knight, Pawn, Queen, Rook

    public abstract class Piece
extends java.lang.Object
    Basis for a Piece within a PieceSet for a Player within a Game. (Chess) Instances of subclasses of Piece are owned by PieceSet.
    Version:
    Mar 3, 2019
    Author:
    gemuelealudino, patricknogaj
